<div type="definition">
<p>SITUATION APPROPRIATE FOR ACHIEVING something.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. The current word for an opportunity presenting itself is shí 時.</p>
<p>2. Huì 會 refers to a coincidental opportunity.</p>
        </div>
<div type="modern-chinese-criteria">
<p>機會</p>
<p>火候</p>
<p>時機</p>
<p>天時</p>
